<br>
The other problems with the bb being in too late all revolved around server patches or resets and the resulting wait for a gm to repop the zone, which again are instances that are out of the ordinary.<br>
<br>
Each case has to be looked at separately, but it seems that the bb guilds are not bound by the 2am rule. Of course in theory, at least in fear, only Cazic and perhaps the temple should still be up so who cares what time they show up.  This is not always the case, and no matter how you look at it if the bb is in the plane much later than 2am it is to be blamed on the guild who had the plane and they will have to bear the consequences. <br>
<br>
My own personal feelings are that at 2am the guild who gets the god loot (minus the epic peices) should change, but this is rather hard to put into place. If that guild no longer get the loot, then they may not stay to help which leads to the bb being in the zone that much later. The next day guild may not be present at 2am to actually get the loot. <br>
<br>
It's just a hard thing to call =(<br>
<br>
it could also be the ones who are supposed to have access to this board do not. I'll check that out tomorrow (ohps <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
