<br>
* 2 AM PST deadline to leave the plane unless BB is called<br>
* 5 AM PST deadline to leave if BB is called in before 2 AM.<br>
* After 5 AM PST, all non epic items belong to the next scheduled group.  Even if none are present, all droppable god items are held by the BB guild and presented to the next day's alliance.<br>
<br>
The goal is 1) to never leave a god up, and 2) to not interfere with the next day's raid.  It could possibly allow a guild to call in a BB guild to clear the plane just to get no drop armor; but usually people are up all night for the god drops. <p>Elaundar Nobillium
